==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Santalic
<hw>San*tal"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of, pertaining to, or obtained from, sandalwood
(<gen>Santalum</gen>); -- used specifically to designate an acid
obtained as a resinous or red crystalline dyestuff, which is called also
<xex>santalin</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Santalin</ent>⟦br⟧
